WEBVTT

00:04:32.760 --> 00:04:35.136
If you speak more than one language,

00:04:35.160 --> 00:04:36.360
please stand up.

00:04:41.320 --> 00:04:42.896
If you have light skin,

00:04:42.920 --> 00:04:44.120
please stand up.

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:55.040
Your glasses meant
that you could afford health care.

00:04:56.960 --> 00:05:01.440
That second or third language you spoke
indicated your elite education.